title.rendered: What if Dumpster Runs Out of Space?

content.rendered:
If Dumpster runs out of storage space, you’ll receive a notification that will alert you. To continue using Dumpster, you’ll need to free up space on your device, or within Dumpster to keep saving files.

We recommend reading this article on tips on optimizing device storage.
